Style:

1. VUE Global SCSS Variables -- DONE
2. remove & add ampersand in scss where unnecessary or necessary -- DONE
3. Remove unnecessary classes, replace them with already existing selectors e.g.: remove .section and use the section tag instead etc -- DONE
4. Customize custom classes rather than bootstrap classes -- DONE
5. Make every styling file to scss -- DONE
6. Make sidenav into flexbox

Anti vue:

- Get rid of jquery
- Use computed instead stuff like this: this.$refs.sortby.innerText = target.innerText
- Vuex store instead window variables
- Unsubscribe from events
- make :class parameters more effective 
- make the formatting unified (" => ', function(){} => ()=>{} etc )